### Get project by id (подставь id)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/projects/{{projectId}}

### ====== POST ======

### Archive project
POST http://localhost:3000/api/projects/{{projectId}}/archive

### Unarchive Project
POST http://localhost:3000/api/projects/{{projectId}}/unarchive

### ====== PATCH ======

PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/projects/{{projectIdForPatch}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Свитер (v3)",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###

PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/projects/{{projectIdForPatch}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "FINISHED"
}

### PATCH project: description only
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectIdForPatch}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "descriptionMd": "## План\n- реглан\n- рукава\n"
}

### PATCH project: yarn plan only
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectIdForPatch}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "yarnPlan": "Drops Alpaca, 6 мотков"
}

### PATCH project: set dates (ISO)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startedAt": "2026-01-15T10:00:00.000Z",
  "finishedAt": null
}

### PATCH project: link to original (basedOnProjectId) - если поле есть в схеме
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectIdForPatch}}
Content-Type: application/json

 {
   "basedOnProjectId": "{{projectId}}"
 }
